Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:04.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(みんな)う～ん…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.47,Main03,ALL,0,0,0,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:08.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ わかっちゃったわ ｵﾚ…\Nすごいの 思いついちゃったわ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:06.24,Main03,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,Oh! I thought of something great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.57,Main03,,0,0,0,,This doesn't…
